Improve the Efficiency of List Creators with the Record Status Filter

With the new default Record Status filter, list creators can immediately focus on the active actionable list member records without applying the filter each time. The filter hides the suppressed and inactive actionable list member records.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in clouds where Actionable List Members is available.

Who: To use the Record Status filter in Actionable List Members, list creators need the Industry Sales Excellence add-on license and the Actionable Segmentation permission set.

How: To see the Record Status filter applied by default, list creators must open an actionable list from the Actionable List list view.
title: Improve Efficiency of List Creators with Record Status Filter
